name: PS-17_g. MetaBall-Pseudorandom[25]B&W
description: v4W.ENko - "PS-17_g. MetaBall-Pseudorandom[25]B&W". The basic "PseudoRandom" is generating 25 vertices to continue the visual story about the "MetaBall Algorithm". The only grayscale gamma is used.  "Pattern Standardization" series is upgraded with more complicated "MetaBall" structure and generating the form such as the "Abstract michro-scheme". The "links-lines" of the "metaball" charge centers  are generated with "Delaunay triangulation".
